(2, 55, 0, 5, 1249368885, 'Summit新增欄位步驟', '1.	先停掉該環境之service，以確保沒有connection在上面\n2.	開啟Summit Launcher的相同環境之DOS mode\n3.	切換到[color=#0000FF]D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\src\\stk\\rtdata\\XXXX[/color]目錄（XXXX為自己建立之目錄）\n4.	執行命令：[color=#FF0000]convertdb -U sumcds51 -F metadata.sql.changes[/color]\n5.	檢查該目錄”[color=#800000]script.out.日期_時間_1.txt[/color]”之內容(最下方)，確認是否成功。\n6.	執行命令：[color=#FF0000]genmeta -U sumcds51[/color]\n7.	Copy 該目錄[b] *.h[/b]及[b] *.incl[/b]兩類檔案至[color=#0040BF]D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\include [/color]Replace原來的檔案\n8.	Copy 該目錄所有檔案至上一層[color=#0040FF]D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\src\\stk\\rtdata[/color] Replace原來的檔案\n9.	執行命令：[color=#FF0000]convertdb -U sumcds51 -F metadata.sql.applychanges[/color]\n10.	檢查該目錄”[color=#800000]script.out.日期_時間_2.txt[/color]”之內容(最下方)，確認是否成功。'),
(3, 55, 0, 10, 1265619645, 'UBS SC安裝及設定說明', 'UBS SC安裝及設定說明請參閱附件。'),
(7, 58, 0, 5, 1486088805, 'dtemodule import trade 失敗處理方式', '1.當Log 出現以下訊息\nError: Transition for this state/action (    _Y/DO    ) is not defined. Please check STD (State Transition Diagram) BFLSTD3.\nError happened when calling sEntityCheckSTDAction: entity=\'FUTURE_TR\', action=\'DO    \'\nFuture Trade Create Error\n\n2.\n[code]\nif(sEntityDoSTDAction(FutureEntity, FutureTrade, NULL, sACT_SAVE, 00) == sSUCCESS)\n{\n	sLogMessage(&quot;Future Trade Created, TradeID = %s&quot;, sLOG_INFO, 0, FutureTrade-&gt;TradeID.Num);\n	\n	cCreateElement(outDocument, statusEl, &quot;Status&quot;, &quot;Success&quot;);\n	response-&gt;appendChild(statusEl);\n}\n[/code]');
