(59, 58, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.12.129', 1248862496, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit Entity Write', '<r>Summit Command:<br/>\ns_base:EntityWrite<br/>\n<br/>\n&lt;Request&gt;<br/>\n&lt;Mode Type=\"xsd:int\"&gt;&lt;/Mode&gt;<br/>\n&lt;Entity&gt;***SUMMIT-XML***&lt;/Entity&gt;<br/>\n&lt;/Request&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n\"Mode\" will be passed through to the Mode paramter of the STK sEntityDBWrite function. Mode can have the following<br/>\nvalues -<br/>\n<br/>\n(00): Default mode - Attempt update first; if update fails, do insert <br/>\n(01): Update mode - Attempt update only <br/>\n(02): Insert mode - Attempt insert only <br/>\nIf left empty (&lt;Mode&gt;&lt;/Mode&gt;), default mode 00 will be used.<br/>\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>&lt;Request&gt;\n   &lt;Mode Type=\"xsd:int\"&gt;00&lt;/Mode&gt;\n   &lt;Entity&gt;\n      &lt;cFCDPD&gt;\n         &lt;cTradeID&gt;12345&lt;/cTradeID&gt;\n         &lt;cPricingDate&gt;20090227&lt;/cPricingDate&gt;\n         &lt;cMTMAmount TYPE=\"Numeric\"&gt;2000000.0&lt;/cMTMAmount&gt;\n      &lt;/cFCDPD&gt;\n   &lt;/Entity&gt;\n&lt;/Request&gt;<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'a06fefd2b35c9964116318260dd5617c', 0, 'AIA=', '1vqi46o7', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(60, 59, 5, 55, 0, '10.48.1.188', 1249369076, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit新增欄位步驟', '<r>1.	先停掉該環境之service，以確保沒有connection在上面<br/>\n2.	開啟Summit Launcher的相同環境之DOS mode<br/>\n3.	切換到<COLOR color=\"#0040BF\"><s>[color=#0040BF]</s>D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\src\\stk\\rtdata\\XXXX<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>目錄（XXXX為自己建立之目錄）<br/>\n4.	執行命令：<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>convertdb -U sumcds51 -F metadata.sql.changes<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n5.	檢查該目錄”<COLOR color=\"#800000\"><s>[color=#800000]</s>script.out.日期_時間_1.txt<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>”之內容(最下方)，確認是否成功。<br/>\n6.	執行命令：<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>genmeta -U sumcds51<e>[/color]</e></COLOR> <br/>\n7.	Copy 該目錄 <B><s>[b]</s>*.h<e>[/b]</e></B>及<B><s>[b]</s> *.incl<e>[/b]</e></B>兩類檔案至<COLOR color=\"#0040BF\"><s>[color=#0040BF]</s>D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\include<e>[/color]</e></COLOR> Replace原來的檔案<br/>\n8.	Copy 該目錄所有檔案至上一層<COLOR color=\"#0040BF\"><s>[color=#0040BF]</s>D:\\sumapps\\V5.1.1\\client\\FEIB_CDS\\src\\stk\\rtdata <e>[/color]</e></COLOR>Replace原來的檔案<br/>\n9.	執行命令：<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>convertdb -U sumcds51 -F metadata.sql.applychanges<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n10.	檢查該目錄”<COLOR color=\"#800000\"><s>[color=#800000]</s>script.out.日期_時間_2.txt<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>”之內容(最下方)，確認是否成功。</r>', '7a9a1d3099354eb59941f34cb18c15de', 0, 'Qg==', '14fqztbs', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0);
