(116, 107, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.12.129', 1299747639, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '修改Summit帳號密碼方式', '<r>使用addsummitlogin的程式<br/>\n<br/>\n先定義檔案的格式如下：<br/>\nInterId    ExterId    DBPass    SummitPass<br/>\n<br/>\n再用addSummitLogin.exe -F ChangePass.txt<br/>\n<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s><br/>\n記得要修改的帳號必需在Summit內已經有建立User才可以修改<br/>\n修改時，帳號/密碼，請使用該環境的帳號密碼如sumdev53/sumdev53<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n<br/>\n請參考Sample File <ATTACHMENT filename=\"sum.txt\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>sum.txt<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '8852dead05290a5589f8a07766c1fa79', 1, 'Agg=', '1qc4otfl', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(117, 108, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.12.129', 1301567745, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '當Summit產生Broker Fee的錯誤時解決方式', '<r>因為此Function為客制化的功能，而且只能在Classic上增加，所以要先注意是否有cBRKFEES.cl<br/>\n附件檔ap-defaults.rar有客制化所有的cl，可以直接放在Sparse Tree下的lib\\app-defaults內即可\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"app-defaults.rar\" index=\"3\"><s>[attachment=3]</s>app-defaults.rar<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"BKFee1.jpg\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>BKFee1.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n首先要進入Classic的畫面進行增加的作業。<br/>\n選擇Database-&gt;Core Static-&gt;Broker\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"BKFee2.jpg\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>BKFee2.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"BKFee3.jpg\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>BKFee3.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '39288dca386e1392ee38df4846eaf858', 1, 'AAg=', '2yuo8thz', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(118, 109, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.12.129', 1304660504, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit 刪除 HKD/CNY Currency Pair', '<t>select * from dmQUOTED_SPOT_DATE where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\';<br/>\nselect * from dmQUOTED_POS_DETAIL where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'; <br/>\nselect * from dmQUOTED  where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\';<br/>\n<br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED_SPOT_DATE where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\';<br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED_POS_DETAIL where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'; <br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED  where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\';<br/>\n<br/>\ncommit;<br/>\n<br/>\nselect * from dmQUOTED_SPOT_DATE where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\n0 rows selected<br/>\n <br/>\n <br/>\nselect * from dmQUOTED_POS_DETAIL where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\n                          AUDIT_VERSION CCY1 CCY2 LOCATION     PLCCY SPOTSPLITCC<br/>\n--------------------------------------- ---- ---- ------------ ----- -----------<br/>\n                                      2 HKD  CNY  DBU          HKD              <br/>\n                                      2 HKD  CNY  OBU          HKD              <br/>\n2 rows selected<br/>\n <br/>\n <br/>\nselect * from dmQUOTED  where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\nAUDIT_ID AUDIT_TABLE                           AUDIT_VERSION AUDIT_CURRENT AUDIT<br/>\n-------- ----------- --------------------------------------- ------------- -----<br/>\n00000033 QUOTED                                            2 Y             VER  <br/>\n1 row selected<br/>\n <br/>\n <br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED_SPOT_DATE where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\n0 rows deleted<br/>\n <br/>\n <br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED_POS_DETAIL where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\n2 rows deleted<br/>\n <br/>\n <br/>\ndelete dmQUOTED  where ccy1 = \'HKD\' and ccy2 = \'CNY\'<br/>\n1 rows deleted</t>', 'a20ea82d57c718b75b0065f309ee96b1', 0, '', 'vgwfp5nz', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(119, 110, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1304902301, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'FEIB Training TRS', '<r>Hi Jerry,<br/>\n<br/>\n <br/>\n<br/>\nPlease refer to the attached file for the training slide of final version.<br/>\n<br/>\nThe following answers are the feedback from the questions raised by user during the training, please send to the related users.<br/>\n<br/>\nCan TRS price reset be done by bulk reset? è No, it needs to do a Price reset trade by trade. <br/>\nWhat’s the Price/Yield method for a Zero Coupon Bond? è Price/Yield Method should put as “DISCP” and Put Pay Freq as “Z”. Please refer to the following setup. \n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"image001.jpg\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>image001.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\nThe TRS termsheet which provided by user can not be booked in TRS trade. The reason is: The TRS trade embedded a CCY swap trade and this term can not be booked in TRS trade. Where TRS trade only supports the reference underlying is a Bond and the funding leg is a fixed or floating index. Therefore the CCS embedded TRS trade can not be booked in TRS.</r>', '887393aa688548a2e84bb8f935149312', 1, 'AAg=', 'fgetd1gi', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
