(262, 233, 36, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1346222591, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit 5.6 功能介紹投影片', '<t>Agenda:<br/>\n介紹v5.6版Equity function &amp; new function<br/>\nfunction 如下=&gt;<br/>\nEquity是否提供<br/>\n  (1)Broker fee rate→券商依成交金額設定手續費級距<br/>\n  (2)Transaction Tax→以賣出成交金額千分之三計算稅額<br/>\n  (3)放空部位額度限制<br/>\n  (4)同ㄧ天同ㄧ支股票需同時除息與除權(發放現金和股票股利)<br/>\n  (5)查詢關係人公司<br/>\n  (6)個股設定投資上限<br/>\nMarket Risk Limits Module=&gt;即時產生P/L、即時控管與發送email及訊息<br/>\nCredit Limit Risk Management<br/>\nBI Module<br/>\nSWIFT Comfirmation Matching<br/>\nNostro management<br/>\nMUST function</t>', '6fa8c91c389d904177b9e2ec9a454696', 1, '', '2ei68kt5', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
