(367, 326, 48, 54, 0, '10.48.1.106', 1392173171, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit upgrade v5.7 library memo', '<r>Compile 舊程式於v5.7版環境注意事項如下：<br/>\n<br/>\n1.sSERIOUS, sINVALID or sFATAL已不再使用, 請改用sLOG_TRACE, sLOG_DEBUG, sLOG_INFO, sLOG_WARNING, sLOG_ERROR and sLOG_FATAL<br/>\n<br/>\n2.mLogMessage在v5.6之前就不再使用，需轉換為sLogMessage。<br/>\n以下有2個方法可以解決<br/>\n(1)於自定mLogMessage macro<br/>\n#define mLogMessage(x)  sLogMessage( (x), sLOG_ERROR, 0 )<br/>\n<br/>\n(2)使用Visual Studio的regular expression將mLogMessage()置換成sLogMessage().<br/>\nFind - <br/>\nmLogMessage{:b@}\\({:b@}{.@}{:b@}{\\n@}{:b@}{.@}{:b@}\\){:b@};<br/>\nReplace With -<br/>\nsLogMessage(\\3\\4\\5\\6\\7, sLOG_ERROR, 0);<br/>\n<br/>\n3.部份include header可能要調整，例如替換為#include &lt;client/stkpublicapi.h&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n4.<ATTACHMENT filename=\"64_bit_porting_references .pdf\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>64_bit_porting_references .pdf<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', 'b4931ae85ea0a0332975b20584c15043', 1, 'AAg=', '3v8ndm34', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
