(391, 343, 11, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1398393205, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '查看Port是誰占用', '<t>通常無法瀏覽有很多種原因, 其中一個是使用的PORT被佔用, <br/>\n網頁預設使用80PORT, FTP為21, POP3為110, MYSQL為3306, MSSQL為1433, 1434等.... 所以可能預設的PORT被別的程式佔用, 這時我們可以先查詢目前電腦PORT使用的情形來做排除<br/>\n<br/>\n1. 查詢命令：netstat - ano, 查詢PID<br/>\n在 \"開始\" =&gt; \"執行\" 下鍵入 cmd 會跳出 \"命令提示字元視窗\", 再輸入上面命令 nestat -ano 會列出目前電腦使用PORT的情形, 我們先查詢佔用程式的PID值</t>', '7de9cbfd7993db00df84364f2509be29', 0, '', '5qocwgu6', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(392, 344, 48, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1399874711, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '設定EToolkitAPI連接', '<r>因為此64Bit API可能有Bug，所以會使用EXCEL_ETOOLKIT為APP連入Summit<br/>\n原本的ETOOLKITSVR_2K卻無法使用，因此解決的方式是在Application Definition直接呼叫出ETOOLKITSVR_2K\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"1.jpg\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>1.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n接下來另存為EXCEL_ETOOLKIT\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2.jpg\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>2.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n此時Administration已經可以使用，但一般User也必需提供該Application的權限，因此我們使用Roles Administration將EXCEL_ETOOLKIT給予該群組權限。\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"3.jpg\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>3.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', 'd8a574f97a25fac8bc1bd10138e5c7e8', 1, 'AAg=', 'j459yei9', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(393, 345, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1400064155, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'How to create Soap On Summit', '<r>Create Soap Service<br/>\n1. Edit setclasspath.bat<br/>\nsumapps\\tools\\Tomcat6.0.16\\bin\\setclasspath.bat<br/>\n<br/>\n--&gt;開始增加(記得要依照HostName進行修改)<br/>\n:setClassPath<br/>\n<br/>\nset \"CLASSPATH=%CLASSPATH%;%CATALINA_HOME%\\bin\\tomcat-juli.jar;%JAVA_HOME%\\lib\\tools.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\art\\art\\1.3\\art-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\common\\concurrency\\1.3\\concurrency-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\common\\ifc\\1.3\\ifc-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\lease\\1.3\\lease-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\java_poa\\1.3\\java_poa-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\java_orb\\1.3\\java_orb-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\naming_service\\1.3\\naming_service-daemon_shared-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\naming_service\\1.3\\naming_service-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\common\\management\\1.3\\management-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\java_mgmt_plugin\\1.3\\java_mgmt_plugin-rt.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\java_transports\\1.3\\iiop.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\ajp\\1.3\\ajp.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\generic_server\\1.3\\app_services.jar;%IT_PRODUCT_DIR%\\lib\\platform\\java_transports\\1.3\\codeset.jar;D:\\sumapps\\tools\\xml4j_2_0_15\\xml4j.jar;D:\\Sumapps\\V5.3.2\\classes\\etoolkitapi_2k.jar;D:\\Sumapps\\V5.3.2\\etc\\soap;D:\\sumapps\\tools\\soap-2_3_1\\lib\\soap.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\mail-1.4.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\servlet-api.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\activation-1.1.jar\"<br/>\n<br/>\nset JAVA_OPTS=-Dorg.omg.CORBA.ORBClass=com.iona.corba.art.artimpl.ORBImpl -Dorg.omg.CORBA.ORBSingletonClass=com.iona.corba.art.artimpl.ORBSingleton -DORBproduct_dir=\"D:\\Sumapps\\tools\\orbixE2A-6.3SP3\" -DORBconfig_domains_dir=\"D:\\Sumapps\\tools\\orbix\\880pca073\\orbix63sp3\\etc\\domains\" -DORBdomain_name=\"orbix63sp3\" -DORBlicense_file=\"D:\\Sumapps\\tools\\orbixE2A-6.3SP3\\etc\\license.txt\"<br/>\n<br/>\ngoto end<br/>\n--&gt;結束增加<br/>\n<br/>\ncopy file activation-1.1.jar &amp; mail-1.4.jar to  D:\\Sumapps\\tools\\tomcat6.0.16\\lib<br/>\n<br/>\nDeploy soap.war on Tomcat <br/>\nThe etoolkitapi_2k.jar &amp; etoolkitapi_websphere.jar on the D:\\sumapps\\V5.3.2\\classes<br/>\ncopy file activation-1.1.jar &amp; mail-1.4.jar &amp; etoolkitapi_2k.jar &amp; etoolkitapi_websphere.jar to  D:\\Sumapps\\tools\\tomcat6.0.16\\webapps\\soap\\WEB-INF\\lib<br/>\n<br/>\nStart Tomcat<br/>\n<br/>\nBrowser <URL url=\"http://localhost:8085/soap/\">http://localhost:8085/soap/</URL><br/>\n<br/>\nModify D:\\Sumapps\\V5.3.2\\etc\\soap\\deploy.cmd<br/>\n<br/>\n--&gt;開始修改(記得要依照HostName進行修改)<br/>\n@echo off<br/>\necho This utility assumes a server URL of <URL url=\"http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter\">http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter</URL><br/>\nif \"%JAVA_HOME%\"==\"\" goto Env<br/>\nif \"%CATALINA_HOME%\"==\"\" goto Env<br/>\nif \"%SOAP_HOME%\"==\"\" goto Env<br/>\nset PATH=%PATH%;%JAVA_HOME%\\bin<br/>\nset CLASSPATH=%SOAP_HOME%\\lib\\soap.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\xerces.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\mail-1.4.jar;%CATALINA_HOME%\\lib\\activation-1.1.jar<br/>\necho %CLASSPATH%<br/>\necho Deploying the eToolkit service...<br/>\njava org.apache.soap.server.ServiceManagerClient <URL url=\"http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter\">http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter</URL> deploy Deploy.xml<br/>\necho .<br/>\necho Verify that it\'s there<br/>\njava org.apache.soap.server.ServiceManagerClient <URL url=\"http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter\">http://880pca073:8085/soap/servlet/rpcrouter</URL> list<br/>\ngoto end<br/>\n:Env<br/>\necho <br/>\necho The following environment variables<br/>\necho    JAVA_HOME<br/>\necho    CATALINA_HOME<br/>\necho    SOAP_HOME<br/>\necho are required to run this utility. Please make sure they are<br/>\necho set and point to where the java, tomcat and the soap package<br/>\necho are installed.<br/>\n:end<br/>\n--&gt;結束修改<br/>\n<br/>\nMake sure your Summit Launcher Include Environment of JAVA_HOME &amp; CATALINA_HOME &amp; SOAP_HOME</r>', 'fb996f199d6ea6ec759c21edf6823150', 0, '', '1y3mdxkv', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
