(411, 360, 37, 61, 0, '10.48.1.132', 1408412542, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'CB Server重開機檢查項目', '<t>CB Server: 10.48.101.73(.75為備援套)<br/>\n檢查項目:<br/>\n   1.工作排程<br/>\n        (1)檢查4個奇唯trade service是否啟動。<br/>\n      (2)檢查FixConsole是否啟動。<br/>\n<br/>\n   2.服務<br/>\n        (1)檢查CB Batch是否啟動。<br/>\n        (2)檢查Syspower FixNet Client是否啟動。</t>', '269abaf54e4cc8c1c762712428754f76', 0, '', '1yc5mfsi', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(412, 360, 37, 53, 0, '10.48.12.129', 1408415394, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: CB Server重開機檢查項目', '<t>經8/18 VM發生問題，有發現到當服務顯示啟動時，並非代表真正啟動。<br/>\n因此Syspower FixNet 的部份還需與奇唯 Roger確認該線路是否正常連線。<br/>\n<br/>\n奇唯聯絡方式 25066667 # 504 Roger</t>', '805d7cb96dd578905813f91561eafbfb', 0, '', '1lwo5p05', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(413, 361, 48, 62, 0, '10.48.2.154', 1408419420, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Fixed Single Name CDS Trade couldn\'t validate', '<r>升級 Summit 5.7 後，發生 Single Name CDS 新交易無法覆核問題，經良哥說明後，整理如下<br/>\n<br/>\n錯誤截圖：\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"01.png\" index=\"3\"><s>[attachment=3]</s>01.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n官方說明文件如下\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2014-08-19_10-00-51.png\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>2014-08-19_10-00-51.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n解決方式：<br/>\n1.) 先在 SummitFT =&gt; MUST Product Group Definition 中，建立『SN_CDS』\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2014-08-19_10-02-21.png\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>2014-08-19_10-02-21.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n2.) 開啟 summit Launcher 對映環境 Cmmand Mode，並匯入 D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\etc\\cd_core_mps\\cds_imm_drule.xml \n<CODE><s>[code]</s>static_import -I cds_imm_drule.xml -NEWACT IMLIVE -UPDACT IMPEDT -XML -FIELDVAL<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n確認正確後，將 -FIELDVAL 改成 -COMMIT\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"02.jpg\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>02.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n完成！重新再測交易 Validate！</r>', '153a2d3a1aa86093e6329fc3c67684be', 1, 'AIg=', '26itznch', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(415, 362, 21, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1409814964, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Credit Service Cold start', '<t>1.Create Cold start script:<br/>\nex:Cold_CSServer.sql<br/>\n內容：<br/>\nspool t:\\Batch\\sumprod\\Cold_StartCS.txt<br/>\ndelete from dmCRDSRVCFG<br/>\n/<br/>\ncommit<br/>\n/<br/>\nspool off<br/>\nexit<br/>\n<br/>\n2.Create run command:<br/>\nex:PurgeCredit.cmd<br/>\n內容：<br/>\nsqlplus sumut01/sumut01@SMDBPROD @D:\\sumapps\\Batch\\sumut01\\Cold_CSServer.sql</t>', '73c44cf3fe57a52ca1cff80593640fa3', 0, '', '2n9n28kn', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
