(419, 365, 26, 64, 0, '10.48.2.160', 1414997940, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Margin AP 切換操作步驟', '<r>AP 101.7(正式) 切換至  101.8(備援) 操作步驟<br/>\n1.) 10.48.101.7 停服務<br/>\n  System7AllStop.bat <br/>\n<br/>\n2.) 10.48.101.74 &lt; RTFS應修正config設定&gt;<br/>\nC:\\Program Files\\FEIB\\RTFSAgent\\RTFSAgent.exe.config<br/>\n        &lt;client&gt;<br/>\n            &lt;endpoint address=\"http://<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>10.48.101.8<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>:27133/VerBank-WSFacade/ws/otherFxTrade\"<br/>\n                binding=\"basicHttpBinding\" bindingConfiguration=\"OtherFxTradePortBinding\"<br/>\n                contract=\"Margin_VerBank.OtherFxTrade\" name=\"OtherFxTradePort\" /&gt;<br/>\n            &lt;endpoint address=\"http://<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>10.48.101.8<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>/WebBank/report\" binding=\"basicHttpBinding\"<br/>\n                bindingConfiguration=\"WebBankPortBinding\" contract=\"Margin_WebBank.WebServer\"<br/>\n                name=\"WebBankPort\" /&gt;<br/>\n        &lt;/client&gt;<br/>\nD:\\FEIB_Web\\RTFS\\web.config<br/>\n&lt;endpoint address=\"http://<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>10.48.101.8<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>:27133/VerBank-WSFacade/ws/otherFxTrade\"<br/>\n    binding=\"basicHttpBinding\" bindingConfiguration=\"OtherFxTradePortBinding\"<br/>\n    contract=\"Margin_VerBank.OtherFxTrade\" name=\"OtherFxTradePort\" /&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n3.) 10.48.101.8 啟服務<br/>\n  System7AllRestart.bat<br/>\n<br/>\n4.) 10.48.10.44 &lt;Gateway1&gt;<br/>\nApplication Layer Gateway Service 切換:<br/>\n桌面捷徑:Stop_FETP_10.7_GateWay(RunAsAdmin)Shortcut<br/>\n桌面捷徑:Start_FETP_10.8_GateWay(RunAsAdmin)Shortcut<br/>\n<br/>\n5.) 10.48.10.45 &lt;Gateway2&gt;<br/>\nApplication Layer Gateway Service 切換:<br/>\n桌面捷徑:Stop_FETP_10.7_GateWay(RunAsAdmin)Shortcut<br/>\n桌面捷徑:Start_FETP_10.8_GateWay(RunAsAdmin)Shortcut<br/>\n<br/>\n6.) 10.48.101.8 啟動 task job服務(AP Restart )<br/>\n     10.48.101.7 暫停task job服務(AP Restart )</r>', '1a08e249c