(463, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735376, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '(未解決)Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<t>目前只要交易進行Barrier Crossing之後，帳務即無問題。<br/>\n交易若不進行Full Termination Action的動作時，月底會產生MTM，但是Mandy不希望交易在Barrier Crossing之後，還繼續產生MTM的帳務，因此必需手動移除MTM的帳務。<br/>\n不過Barrier Crossing後若要達到此功能，勢必要在系統面先可以判斷是否該交易有被進行Barrier Crossing的記號，如此才可以達到該功能，另外原本相關的報表也必需進行調整。<br/>\n<br/>\n2015/7/15 和Mandy討論後，我們先進行Barrier Crossing確認是否可以判斷該記號，如果可以，再進行下一部的需求討論。</t>', 'faa4bc30da58d73f7d1bf4654bd3c9d0', 0, '', 'o5lphk5z', 1, 1438822411, '', 53, 1, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(464, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735446, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>交易如何進行Terminat方式\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// Execute Fully Terminate \n	sCUST_ID counterparty;\n	sOPTERMPAR oparm;\n\n\nmemset(&amp;oparm, 0, sizeof(sOPTERMPAR));\n			memset(&amp;counterparty, 0, sizeof(sCUST_ID));\n			strcpy(counterparty.Name, temptrade-&gt;Base.Env-&gt;Cust.Name);\n			oparm.Type = sTA_TERMINATED;\n			oparm.TradeDate = sAsOfDate();\n			oparm.EventDate = sMAXUS;\n			oparm.EffDate = sAsOfDate();\n			oparm.counterParty = &amp;counterparty;\n\n			if (sEntityDoSTDAction(sGetEntityByName(\"MUST_TR\"), temptrade, (void *)&amp;oparm, sACT_FULLTERM, 0) != sSUCCESS)\n			{\n				char msg[100];\n				sprintf(msg, \"Do Fully Terminate for Trade %s Failed.\", temptrade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n				sLogMessage(msg, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n			}\n			if (sEntityDoSTDAction(sGetEntityByName(\"MUST_TR\"), temptrade, NULL, sACT_SAVE, 0) != sSUCCESS)\n			{\n				char msg[100];\n				sprintf(msg, \"Do Fully Terminate for Trade %s Failed.\", temptrade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n				sLogMessage(msg, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n			}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'a440aaf7caf843d6e494be41f536c2ac', 0, 'AIA=', '1961huen', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(465, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735476, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>判斷交易是否已完成Barrier Crossing，請參考下列屬性：<br/>\n判斷Back.TermAssignStatus 是否等於 sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>&lt;BACK&gt;\n         &lt;dmOwnerTable&gt;MUST_TR&lt;/dmOwnerTable&gt;\n         &lt;TradeId&gt;378297DB&lt;/TradeId&gt;\n         &lt;TermAssignStatus&gt;BARCRO&lt;/TermAssignStatus&gt;\n         &lt;SchemaId&gt;TRF1&lt;/SchemaId&gt;\n         &lt;TrAcctType&gt;TRADING&lt;/TrAcctType&gt;\n         &lt;SsiByEvent&gt;N&lt;/SsiByEvent&gt;\n         &lt;CLSSettlement&gt;N&lt;/CLSSettlement&gt;\n         &lt;CustomEventRules TYPE=\"EntList\" SINGLE=\"Y\"&gt;\n            &lt;EVNTRULE&gt;&lt;/EVNTRULE&gt;\n         &lt;/CustomEventRules&gt;\n         &lt;AssignmentDetails TYPE=\"EntList\" SINGLE=\"N\"&gt;\n            &lt;TRDASSIGN&gt;\n               &lt;TradeId&gt;378297DB&lt;/TradeId&gt;\n               &lt;dmOwnerTable&gt;MUST_TR&lt;/dmOwnerTable&gt;\n               &lt;AssignDate&gt;20150721&lt;/AssignDate&gt;\n               &lt;TermAssignStatus&gt;BARCRO&lt;/TermAssignStatus&gt;\n               &lt;AssignVersion TYPE=\"Numeric\"&gt;3&lt;/AssignVersion&gt;\n               &lt;EffectiveDate&gt;20150721&lt;/EffectiveDate&gt;\n            &lt;/TRDASSIGN&gt;\n         &lt;/AssignmentDetails&gt;\n&lt;/BACK&gt;<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '925d373da12cf51f71256ce430150594', 0, 'AIA=', '3qfb9m4f', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(466, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735550, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>在FxOptionMustReport.cc內略過Barrier Crossing的報表<br/>\n主要的判斷為確認交易目前是否在Barrier Crossing的狀態，若是的話，就略過此交易，不產生在報表上面<br/>\n<br/>\n請於第182行加上下列程式<br/>\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// Write By Tomy 20150803 , Skip Barrier Crossing\n        if(trade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING)\n            continue;<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'bfd66de4d92ae05cc28229330ed86703', 0, 'AIA=', '1sw6t5tb', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(467, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735647, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>在extacctevent_feib.cc內略過Barrier Crossing於月底時，不要產生MTM Event<br/>\n會計帳在產生MTM的時候，原本為Terminate狀態下即交易到期，因此不會產生任何的MTM，不過，因為後台需要在Barrier Crossing的時候就不要產生，因此在會計帳產生MTM時，一併略過Barrier Crossing的狀態。<br/>\n請於第2974行加上下列程式\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// Write By Tomy 20150803 , Skip Barrier Crossing\n            if(Trade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING)\n            {\n                cRemoveEvent(Trade, AcctngEventL, sAE_MTM);\n                sprintf(buf, \" TradeID &lt;%s&gt; is Barrier Crossing, Skip MTM!!\\n\", Trade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n                sLogMessage(buf, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n            }<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'df9037fb152ebb674dde48a09d7d0071', 0, 'AIA=', '1uxnkwwk', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(468, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438735809, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'stpClientModule2內調整交易到期日', '<r>在stpClientModule2.cc內，透過STP略過需要放行的交易：<br/>\n讓TradeBlotter可以顯示正確的到期日，<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>不過因為Credit Maturity Date 是參考Fixing Schedule 的最後一期，因此目前尚無法修正<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>。<br/>\n<br/>\n用於只要是ituser(意味系統產生MUST 的Terminate交易)，STP在判斷為ituser的情況下，就不用產生雙人覆核的Exception。<br/>\n因為原本會有兩組AlwaysException產生，會要後台的經辦和主管放行。<br/>\n<br/>\n請於865行加上下列程式：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>sUSER * user = sUser();\n// Skip Must Full Terminate when user equal ituser , Write By Tomy 20150804\n    if(strcmp(user-&gt;UserID.ID,\"ituser\") ==0)\n        if(pTrade-&gt;Base.TradeType == sTT_MUST &amp;&amp; strcmp(pTrade-&gt;Base.Env-&gt;Folder.Name,\"FXFWD\") == 0)\n        {\n            if(pTrade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_TERMINATED){\n                sLogMessage(\"We will skip exception of \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' for Full Terminal, The Trade ID %s\", sLOG_INFO, 0, pTrade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n                return sSUCCESS;\n            }\n        }<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n請在SU_CreditLimitCheck內 判斷MUST的部份 加上：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// Write By Tomy 20150805 , 當交易偵測到有Barrier Crossing的動作的時候，就將原始的到期日改成Barrier Crossing Date\n		if(pTrade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING)\n        {\n			sLogMessage(\"Must TradeId = %s , Check Barrier Crossing Status -- Start \", sLOG_INFO, 0);\n			sTRDASSIGN * TradeAssignmentDetail;\n			sIDATE BarrierCrossingDate = sAsOfDate();\n			for ( int i=0; i&lt;pTrade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;AssignmentDetails.List.ItemsUsed; i++) {\n				TradeAssignmentDetail = ( sTRDASSIGN * )sGetListItem( &amp;pTrade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;AssignmentDetails, i );\n				if (!TradeAssignmentDetail) {\n					sLogMessage(\"Unable to get the list item\", sLOG_INFO, 0);\n					exit (sERROR);\n				}\n\n				// 記錄 BarrierCrossing的時間\n				if(TradeAssignmentDetail-&gt;TermAssignStatus ==  sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING)\n				{\n					SU_MUST_API *mustapi = SU_MUST_API::MUST_API_Create(pTrade, sGetEntityByName(\"MUST_TR\"));\n					sSU_MUSTAPI_Constant compValue;\n					sSI_COMP_NAME compName;\n					strcpy(compName.Name , \"OTC_END\");\n					// 查詢該變數型態\n					sOPERAND_TYPE VarColumnType= mustapi-&gt;GetVariableType(compName);\n					// 將資料放入指定容器\n					int ret = compValue.SetResult( VarColumnType, (void *) &amp;BarrierCrossingDate);\n					// 將變數改為容器內容\n					ret = mustapi-&gt;SetVariableConstant(compValue, compName);\n\n					char DateBuf[10];\n					sGCDate(DateBuf,BarrierCrossingDate );\n\n					sLogMessage(\"Must TradeId = %s , Change OTC_END Parameter , Date is %s , Status = %d \", sLOG_INFO, 0, pTrade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num,DateBuf,ret);\n				}\n			}\n		}<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n產生的記錄如下：<br/>\n\n<QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>2015-08-04 10:59:46.551 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.12\\src\\distcmpnts\\gstp_server\\gstp_workflow_diagram.cc:841] Starting Workflow. Instance Key : MUST_TR/378297DB/MUST /9, Entity Id: 000005DX<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:46.629 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\stpClientModule2\\stpClientModule2.cc:762] Msg TradeId= 378297DB, tradeStatus<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:46.832 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\stpClientModule2\\stpClientModule2.cc:869] We will skip exception for Full Terminal, The Trade ID 378297DB<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:46.832 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\stpClientModule2\\stpClientModule2.cc:869] We will skip exception for Full Terminal, The Trade ID 378297DB<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:46.832 [ERROR] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\stpClientModule2\\stpClientModule2.cc:2335] For MO Credit Limit Check TradeID = 378297DB, TradeType =MUST , ProductType = FXEXO01<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:46.848 [ERROR] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\stpClientModule2\\stpClientModule2.cc:2856] Check Limit Result = WHERE LIMITTYPE=\'CNTPARTY\' AND RISKTYPE=\'CREDIT\' AND GLOBAL=\'Y\' AND AUDIT_CURRENT=\'Y\' AND CUSTOMERID=\'SCBTWN\' <br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:47.597 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.12\\src\\stk\\stptradesrv\\tradewritepolicy.cc:178] STD Action performed on Trade: ACCEPT<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:47.612 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.12\\src\\distcmpnts\\gstp_server\\gstp_workflow_diagram.cc:921] Finished Workflow. Instance Key : MUST_TR/378297DB/MUST /9, Entity Id: 000005DX<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:47.659 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.12\\src\\distcmpnts\\gstp_server\\gstp_workflow_diagram.cc:841] Starting Workflow. Instance Key : MUST_TR/378297DB/MUST /10, Entity Id: 000005DX<br/>\n2015-08-04 10:59:47.659 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.12\\src\\distcmpnts\\gstp_server\\gstp_workflow_diagram.cc:921] Finished Workflow. Instance Key : MUST_TR/378297DB/MUST /10, Entity Id: 000005DX<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE></r>', 'ef9187dfd08e2b65f652c3ffa6bff7f6', 0, 'goA=', '3icit4cl', 1, 1438925354, '', 53, 1, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(469, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438736005, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>在FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc內，略過BarrierCrossing的交易，不要計算額度：<br/>\n額度部份原本也是在交易進行Terminate的時候才會釋放額度，不過現在因為Barrier Crossing的狀態下，就要釋放。<br/>\n另外寫入額度的部份也採用<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s> 010的模式<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>，即代表使用交易方式強制寫入，而且寫入的<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>Results = 0<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>，如此就不用去改Addon的程式。<br/>\n<br/>\n請在416行加上：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// If BarrierCrossing , MUST Create will become 0 , Write by tomy 20150804\n			if(trade-&gt;Base.TradeType == sTT_MUST &amp;&amp; strcmp(trade-&gt;Base.Env-&gt;Folder.Name,\"FXFWD\") == 0)\n			{\n				if(trade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING){\n					exposure = 0.0;\n					if( sCreditSaveResults( Results, trade, Parm, cust, exposure, AsOfDate, mode | 010 )  != sSUCCESS)\n					{\n						sprintf( _Exception, \"Can\'t save results for customer[%s].\", cust-&gt;Id.Name );\n						throw _Exception;\n					}\n					sLogMessage(\"\'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID %s is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.\", sLOG_INFO, 0, trade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n				}\n			}\n			else<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n若略過的訊息如下：<br/>\n\n<QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>2015-08-04 11:53:27.176 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.14\\src\\distcmpnts\\cs\\crdsrvbase\\crdsrv_database.cc:2689] Applying trade: MUST_TR/377542OB/MUST <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.192 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.208 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377542OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.<br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.208 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.223 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377542OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.<br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.223 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.223 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377542OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.<br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.223 [INFO ] [c:\\summit\\acpatchlocal\\win64\\qa\\V5.7\\SERVICEPACK\\V5.7.14\\src\\distcmpnts\\cs\\crdsrvbase\\crdsrv_database.cc:2689] Applying trade: MUST_TR/377543OB/MUST <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.239 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.254 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377543OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.<br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.254 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.254 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377543OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0.<br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.254 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:467] cCreditRiskCalcMethods Calculation Method cMUSTCRED <br/>\n2015-08-04 11:53:27.270 [INFO ] [D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\stk\\client_Credit\\FEIB_mustcreditmodel.cc:424] \'MUST Trade and Folder equal FXFWD\' , The Trade ID 377543OB is BarrierCrossing action be trigger,so credit = 0<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE></r>', '501d2201cb60236251e4312e06116560', 0, 'goA=', 'cqmfeqfx', 1, 1438751950, '', 53, 2, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(470, 406, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438736427, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '(未解決)AresSummit 上傳會計帳有問題', '<r>台北發生日期為7/23和7/30<br/>\n香港發生日期為7/24<br/>\n<br/>\n發生的狀況為僅有交易帳有產生，而下半部損益和兌換帳皆沒有產生，<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>問題是在第6步驟，目前只知道因該是有寫入Table，但無法知道為何在匯整產出的時候出問題<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>。<br/>\n<br/>\n因為AresSummit在產生會計帳的方式步驟如下：<br/>\n1.掃瞄dmpostingevent table<br/>\n2.找尋EXTRACTFLAG不為Y的資料<br/>\n3.將交易帳進行產生成優利需要的格式<br/>\n4.清除cbglac的Table<br/>\n5.遇到下列交易即放入cbglac的Table\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>cbglac.event_type, \"IAC\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"cIAC_BASE\") == 0 || \n            strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"IAM\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"IRC\") == 0 ||\n            strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"MTM\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"NPV\") == 0 ||\n            strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"GPV\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"PVX\") == 0 ||\n            strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"cREAL\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"cREAL_BASE\") == 0 ||\n            strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"cMTM_BASE\") == 0 || strcmp(cbglac.event_type, \"cPL_EXER\") == 0\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n6.將cbglac的資料匯整後一併產出<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\ndmPOSTINGEVENT並不會每筆都撈出來，只有符合下方條件的EVENT才會撈出。\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>select * from dmPOSTINGEVENT where (location=\'DBU\' or accountid like \'DBU%\') and postingdate=\'日期\' and accountid not in (\'CASH_SUSPENSE\',\'SUSPENSE\',\'DUMMYCASH\',\'DUMMY\',\'CONTROL\',\'NETTING\',\'CASH_CONTROL\', \'OBUCONTRAINBR\', \'DBUCONTRAINBR\', \'OBUINTERBR\', \'DBUINTERBR\',\'INTERBR\',\'CONTRAINBR\') and not accountId like \'DUM%\'  <e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n7/30已請DBA進行監控AresSummit的 cbglac，只要有進行Inser,Update,Delete,Select就進行記錄。<br/>\n<br/>\n附檔為台北和港行ReRun的程式，兩個不同是在Imakefile內有定義宣告引用不同的Library，另外make的時候只會產生 exe 和 pdb，exp和lib皆不會產生。\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"SumglfeibReRunByDate.zip\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>SumglfeibReRunByDate.zip<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n上傳檔案內容為台北、香港Rerun的程式。\n<QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>台北ReRun的方式是將該執行檔進行make之後，放置於D:\\AresSummit\\Batch下，並建立一個批次檔，內容如下：<br/>\ncall d:\\AresSummit\\batch\\feib_summit_env.bat<br/>\ncall d:\\AresSummit\\batch\\SumglfeibReRunByDate.exe -rerun 20131002<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE>\n<QUOTE><s>[quote]</s>香港ReRun的方式是將該執行檔進行make之後，放置於D:\\AresSummitHK\\Batch下，並建立一個批次檔，內容如下：<br/>\ncall d:\\AresSummitHK\\batch\\feib_summit_env.bat<br/>\ncall d:\\AresSummitHK\\batch\\SumglfeibReRunByDateHK.exe -rerun 20131002<e>[/quote]</e></QUOTE></r>', 'aa61d8ea202d5cdcad4cda15dad4c4d0', 1, 'gog=', '3ix0lvuu', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(471, 407, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438737914, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '(已解決)電文放行和Dispatch昇級後變成同一個人可以同時覆核', '<r>V5.7昇級的時候，我們有將D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\etc\\scripts\\STD\\std_v5.7.0.CORE重新匯入<br/>\n匯入的指令為<CODE><s>[code]</s>convertdb -F D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\etc\\scripts\\STD\\std_v5.7.0.CORE<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n因為會將所有系統預設的STD全部重建，因此造成原本VER_YES_dispch_DISP_YES的Same user屬性被打勾。<br/>\n<br/>\n處理的方式是將打勾移除後，重新Generate STD，請參考該文件<ATTACHMENT filename=\"設定Document在Verify與Dispatch不可使用同一個User方式.docx\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>設定Document在Verify與Dispatch不可使用同一個User方式.docx<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '5bac3f6b2fb721e118ad919205cd9655', 1, 'AIg=', '9wvjbs71', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(472, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438743128, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>採用批次方式進行Terminal Action<br/>\nT:\\V5.7\\client\\FEIB_TEST\\src\\apps\\FullTerminateAction<br/>\n<br/>\n執行時，記得要將user改成ituser，指令為 set USER=ituser<br/>\n<br/>\n執行指令如下：  fullterminateaction -F FilterName -Day 12 -COMMIT<br/>\n\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"FullTerminateAction.zip\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>FullTerminateAction.zip<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', 'c4ee317c2edb391c8cc313ec10fca79d', 1, 'AAg=', '1pj53jqw', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(473, 405, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438821823, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Must交易能夠不做Full Termination Action', '<r>在交易尚未進行Full Terminate的情況下：<br/>\n<br/>\nMust內若要修改Trade Blotter所顯示的到期日，就必需修改OTC Parameters內的OTC_END的日期內容：\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-06_08-59-26.jpg\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>2015-08-06_08-59-26.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\nMust內若要修改Credit Maturity內所顯示的到期日，就必需修改FXT Component 內的Schedule，因為會顯示最後一期的日期：\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-06_09-01-43.jpg\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>2015-08-06_09-01-43.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n只要移除Fixing Schedule即可\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-06_09-04-12.jpg\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>2015-08-06_09-04-12.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '889a4812d445f7956c75794c7797ca0c', 1, 'AAg=', '28aqh21x', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(474, 408, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1438822301, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '(未解決)前台在進行CB Exercise的交時，所代入必需要執行的交易ID不正確', '<r>20150804下午,該筆交易編號FASO150302017。<br/>\n<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>解決的方式，直接修改匯入交易的XML檔案內的TRADEID，將360319DB改成38322DB，暫時解決問題。<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-04_15-20-43.jpg\" index=\"3\"><s>[attachment=3]</s>2015-08-04_15-20-43.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n交易內容如下：\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-04_15-29-34.jpg\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>2015-08-04_15-29-34.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n正確SUMMIT TRADE ID應該為38322DB\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-04_15-37-45.jpg\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>2015-08-04_15-37-45.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n錯誤對應的SUMMIT TRADE ID 為360319DB\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2015-08-04_15-40-54.jpg\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>2015-08-04_15-40-54.jpg<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '5374b92f9de43ab16fdb8ebb502242d1', 1, 'Agg=', '3uzuq2r1', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
