(507, 429, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1443062104, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '在程式內加上判斷不得重覆執行的方式 C++', '<r>1. 定義該程式的唯一識別碼，該識別碼未來需要管理：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>#define APPLICATION_INSTANCE_MUTEX_NAME \"{BA49C45E-B29A-4359-A07C-51B65B5571AD}\"<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n2. 在 Main 之後進行判斷，若有重覆執行就自我離開：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s> //Make sure at most one instance of the tool is running\n    HANDLE hMutexOneInstance(::CreateMutex( NULL, TRUE, (LPCWSTR)APPLICATION_INSTANCE_MUTEX_NAME));\n    bool bAlreadyRunning((::GetLastError() == ERROR_ALREADY_EXISTS));\n    if (hMutexOneInstance == NULL || bAlreadyRunning)\n    {\n    	if(hMutexOneInstance)\n    	{\n    		::ReleaseMutex(hMutexOneInstance);\n    		::CloseHandle(hMutexOneInstance);\n    	}\n    	printf(\"The application is already running\");\n		return -99;\n    }<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '65bd9fa00d9baa1e5df2f25051e54441', 0, 'AIA=', '3hx849k0', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(508, 430, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443151651, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '基本資料型態與變數', '<r>基本資料型態<br/>\nint : 整數值<br/>\n用來表示一個正整數或負整數(也就是沒有小數點的數字)。<br/>\n<br/>\nFloat : 浮點數<br/>\n包含小數點的值<br/>\nDouble : 浮點數精度的倍數。<br/>\nBOOL : 布林值<br/>\n在Objective-C中是使用YES,NO<br/>\n<br/>\nChar : 字元<br/>\n比較常見的object型態<br/>\nNSString : 字串<br/>\n是一串宇元的組合，且一但被實例化(instantiate)後是不可以變更的。<br/>\n<br/>\n是把C的字串轉換成NSString的簡寫，在需要NSString的地方才需要這個轉化,例如NSLog裡面。<br/>\n在需要C string的地方,還是用\"字串\"的。<br/>\n語法:@\"指定字串\",以雙引號分隔並於字串前加「@」符號<br/>\n例：<br/>\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>title = @\"Hello\";<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\nNSNumber : 一個包裝類別(wrapper class)<br/>\n為將基本型態包裝成數值型態的物件。<br/>\n<br/>\nNSArray(collection)<br/>\n是建立及管理「陣列」的類別。可以使用NSArray來建立一個不可變動的靜態陣列(static array)，如果要建立動態陣列，就要使用NSMutableArray。<br/>\n<br/>\nNSDictionary :<br/>\n和NSArray一樣，為儲存物件的集合，每個項目都是以鍵值(key-value)配對。</r>', 'dcbb5d3463ee838e1e140d40d7aacbf4', 0, 'AIA=', 'xw5v8fot', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(509, 431, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161222, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '指定TableViewCell顯示checkmark', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s><i>\n</i>//顯示點選的row為checkmark\nUITableViewCell *cell = [tableView cellForRowAtIndexPath:indexPath];\ncell.accessoryType = UITableViewCellAccessoryCheckmark;\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'e9a768f3a63bbf30c065858b27923a0a', 0, 'AIA=', '3tjpm0yg', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(510, 432, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161266, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '指定TableViewCell切換成編輯模式', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s><i>\n</i>//將TableView切換成編輯模式\n-(void)tableView:(UITableView *)tableView commitEditingStyle:(UITableViewCellEditingStyle)editingStyle forRowAtIndexPath:(NSIndexPath *)indexPath {\n    //從資料array中刪除列\n    [tableData removeObjectAtIndex:indexPath.row\\];\n     \n    //要求TableView重新更新畫面\n    [tableView reloadData];\n}\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '7b2604344ebc117be67a6de140ba4c57', 0, 'AIA=', '2dw6swi1', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(511, 433, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161524, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '讀取Property List file sample', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>// Find out the path of recipes.plist\nNSString *path = [[NSBundle mainBundle] pathForResource:@\"recipes\" ofType:@\"plist\"];\n \n// Load the file content and read the data into array\nNSDictionary *dict = [[NSDictionary alloc] initWithContentsOfFile:path];\ntableData = [dict objectForKey:@\"RecipeName\"];\nthumbnails = [dict objectForKey:@\"Thumbnail\"];\nprepTime = [dict objectForKey:@\"PrepTime\"];<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '3eda409fa38ec84e8c6d66a6a92d3ed1', 0, 'AIA=', '1d7cc2ej', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(512, 434, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161586, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '指定root ViewController and 客製Xib 檔案', '<r>調整AppDelegate.m檔案<br/>\n\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>- (BOOL)application:(UIApplication *)application didFinishLaunchingWithOptions:(NSDictionary *)launchOptions {\n    // Override point for customization after application launch.\n     \n    //Bind viewController and xib\n    HelloWorldViewController *helloWorldViewController = [[HelloWorldViewController alloc] initWithNibName:@\"HelloWorldViewController\" bundle:nil];\n     \n    self.window.rootViewController = helloWorldViewController;\n     \n    return YES;\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '830032dc09e27bb0ec8a4dbe51f850af', 0, 'AIA=', '239wrpbz', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(513, 435, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161640, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '離開目前View到上一個View', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>[self.presentingViewController dismissViewControllerAnimated:YES completion:nil];<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '97331372cee83159ce133ef9dc4daffb', 0, 'AIA=', '320hq5k1', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(514, 436, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161691, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'textField 檢核輸入資料長度是否為0或未輸入', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>- (BOOL)shouldPerformSegueWithIdentifier:(NSString *)identifier sender:(id)sender{\n    if (![self.nameUITextField.text length]) {\n        [self alertMsg:@\"Name field reqired..!!\"];\n        return NO;\n    }else if (![self.phoneUITextField.text length])\n    {\n        [self alertMsg:@\"Phone field requied..!!\"];\n        return NO;\n    }\n   return YES;\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'a52c6b6eb534c2d9eca16f8e7b737852', 0, 'AIA=', 'rozwe1uo', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(515, 437, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161733, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'textField 呼叫unwind segue方式', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>// 定義textField按了return鍵後，指定unwind segue，使用之前可以在屬性面板中設定return key的屬性\n- (BOOL)textFieldShouldReturn:(UITextField *)textField{\n    if (textField == self.nameUITextField) {\n        [self.nameUITextField resignFirstResponder];\n        [self.phoneUITextField becomeFirstResponder];\n    }else if (textField == self.phoneUITextField){\n        if ([self shouldPerformSegueWithIdentifier:@\"unwind\" sender:self]) {\n            [self performSegueWithIdentifier:@\"unwind\" sender:self];\n        }\n    }\n    return YES;\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'cd5fd0296cf4f812dbab9cf65e571bc4', 0, 'AIA=', 'njaigt43', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(516, 438, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161801, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '跳出警告(alert)訊息框', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>//產生一個UIAlertController，其風格為UIAlertControllerStyleAlert\n//風格亦可以換成UIAlertControllerStyleActionSheet。\nUIAlertController *alertController = [UIAlertController alertControllerWithTitle:@\"Title\" message:@\"我的訊息\" preferredStyle:UIAlertControllerStyleAlert];\n \n//宣告一個「確定」按鈕\nUIAlertAction *okAction = [UIAlertAction actionWithTitle:@\"確定\" style:UIAlertActionStyleDefault handler:^(UIAlertAction *action) {\n        //按鈕按下次後要做的事情寫在這兒\n        [self dismissViewControllerAnimated:YES completion:nil];\n}];\n \n//將確定按鈕加到UIAlertController中\n[alertController addAction:okAction];\n//顯示這個controller，也就是訊息框\n[self presentViewController:alertController animated:YES completion:nil];<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n其他方式：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>//顯示alert訊息\nUIAlertView *messageAlert = [[UIAlertView alloc] initWithTitle:@\"Cell資料被點選了\" message:[tableData objectAtIndex:indexPath.row]  delegate:nil cancelButtonTitle:@\"OK\" otherButtonTitles:nil];\n[messageAlert show];<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'af704994acf5044ab993950204fdaab1', 0, 'AIA=', '3qexr9js', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(517, 439, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443161920, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '不使用segue的畫面切換', '<r><LIST><s>[list]</s>\n<LI>1.新增一個ViewController<br/>\n2.在Identity inspector 面板中的Storyboard ID填入任一個字串，再將Use StoryBoard ID勾起來。<br/>\n3.在原先的ViewController.m中輸入以下代碼:\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>UIViewController *vc = [self.storyboard instantiateViewControllerWithIdentifier:@\"secondView\"];\n[self showDetailViewController:vc sender:self];<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n取消畫面切換，可以使segue暫時失去作用，只要在shouldPerformSegueWithIdentifier方法中回傳NO就可以暫停切換畫面的功能。</LI>\n<e>[/list]</e></LIST></r>', 'ed285202ad9524be2d2e8c9d650b89da', 0, 'AMA=', '3gzdyp90', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(518, 440, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443162076, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '判定裝置總類與取得size資訊', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>if (self.traitCollection.userInterfaceIdiom == UIUserInterfaceIdiomPad) {\n   NSLog(@\"裝置為 iPad\");\n}\nif (self.traitCollection.userInterfaceIdiom == UIUserInterfaceIdiomPhone) {\n   NSLog(@\"裝置為 iPhone\");\n \n// 實作willTransitionToTraitCollection方法，取得當width and height的regular or compact有變化的時候被呼叫。\n// iPad的width and height都被設定成regular，因此iPad的方向有變化時，這個方法不會被呼叫\n- (void)willTransitionToTraitCollection:(UITraitCollection *)newCollection withTransitionCoordinator:(id)coordinator\n{\n    [super willTransitionToTraitCollection:newCollection withTransitionCoordinator:coordinator];\n    if (newCollection.horizontalSizeClass == UIUserInterfaceSizeClassCompact) {\n        NSLog(@\"Compact Width\");\n    }\n    if (newCollection.horizontalSizeClass == UIUserInterfaceSizeClassRegular) {\n        NSLog(@\"Regular Width\");\n    }\n    if (newCollection.verticalSizeClass == UIUserInterfaceSizeClassCompact) {\n        NSLog(@\"Compact Height\");\n    }\n    if (newCollection.verticalSizeClass == UIUserInterfaceSizeClassRegular) {\n        NSLog(@\"Compact Height\");\n    }\n}\n \n// 實作viewWillTransitionToSize方法，當width or height的解析度有改變時會被呼叫。藉由此方式來判斷是直向還是橫向\n- (void)viewWillTransitionToSize:(CGSize)size withTransitionCoordinator:(id)coordinator\n{\n    [super viewWillTransitionToSize:size withTransitionCoordinator:coordinator];\n \n    UIDeviceOrientation orientation = [UIDevice currentDevice].orientation;\n    if (orientation == UIDeviceOrientationLandscapeLeft) {\n        NSLog(@\"橫向，頂端在左側\");\n    }\n    if (orientation == UIDeviceOrientationLandscapeRight) {\n        NSLog(@\"橫向，頂端在右側\");\n    }\n    if (orientation == UIDeviceOrientationPortrait) {\n        NSLog(@\"直向\");\n    }\n    if (orientation == UIDeviceOrientationPortraitUpsideDown) {\n        NSLog(@\"直向，但上下顛倒\");\n    }\n    if (orientation == UIDeviceOrientationUnknown) {\n        NSLog(@\"方向未知\");\n    }\n    NSLog(@\"解析度為 %.0f x %.0f\", size.width, size.height);\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '0a8ce3a587f5eaf2f60644f85eb3d9e3', 0, 'AIA=', '1spr18va', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(519, 441, 50, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443162208, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Objective-C 格式符號', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>%@ : Object\n%d, %i : signed int\n%u : unsigned int\n%f : float/double\n%x, %X : hexadecimal int\n%o : octal int\n%zu : size_t\n%p : pointer\n%e : float/double ( in scientific notation)\n%g : float/double ( as %f or %e, depending on value)\n%s : C string (bytes)\n%S : C string (unichar)\n%c : character\n%C : unichar\n%lld : long long\n%llu : unsigned long long\n%Lf : long double\n%.*s : Pascal string (requires two arguments, pass poster[0] as the first,pstr+1 as the second)<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'bbdf72c16d960a98ee2a8f339509188e', 0, 'AIA=', '389nb2mu', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(520, 442, 22, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1443582221, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'AdvNostro運作方式說明', '<r>AdvNostro規格說明書： <ATTACHMENT filename=\"Advance Nostro Report規格書(第二階段).doc\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>Advance Nostro Report規格書(第二階段).doc<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\nftpget.pl ftp取檔作業<br/>\nGET103.pl 103電文取檔作業<br/>\nGET950.pl 950電文取檔作業<br/>\nMT950LAST.pl 950最後傳送日期計算<br/>\n<br/>\nSummit<br/>\nSwiftParser 從AresSummit取得電文資料<br/>\nNostroDataImport 將電文資料匯入Summit Entity \"NOSTRO\"</r>', '6b0c1cadeccad9b30428d4a91e455839', 1, 'AAg=', '3qt5puq0', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(521, 443, 5, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1443768707, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '透過eToolKit 執行報表並取得資料', '<t>執行報表功能：<br/>\ns_report:ExecuteReport<br/>\n&lt;Request&gt;&lt;applicationid&gt;EXPECTPAY&lt;/applicationid&gt;&lt;parameters&gt;-F BO_OPT_SETTL -X 04/11/14 -Y 12/11/14 -XML&lt;/parameters&gt;&lt;/Request&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n取得報表對應handle資料：<br/>\n&lt;Response&gt;&lt;reporthandle&gt;EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150902102503_19342&lt;/reporthandle&gt;&lt;/Response&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n取得報表執行狀態結果：<br/>\ns_report:GetReportStatus<br/>\n&lt;Request&gt;&lt;mode&gt;SPECIFIED&lt;/mode&gt;&lt;reporthandle&gt;EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150903164729_19342&lt;/reporthandle&gt;&lt;/Request&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n回覆報表執行結果：<br/>\n&lt;Response&gt;<br/>\n   &lt;report commandline=\"expectpay -F BO_OPT_SETTL -X 04/11/14 -Y 12/11/14 -o c:\\summit\\spool\\summitft1\\EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150902102503_19342\\EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150902102503_19342\" endtime=\"20150902 10:27:00\" handle=\"EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150902102503_19342\" resultcode=\"0\" starttime=\"20150902 10:25:03\" status=\"completed\" title=\"Expected Payments Report\"/&gt;<br/>\n&lt;/Response&gt;<br/>\n<br/>\n取得報表執行結果資料：<br/>\ns_report:GetReportResults<br/>\n&lt;Request&gt;&lt;reporthandle&gt;EXPECTPAY_summitft1_20150902102503_19342&lt;/reporthandle&gt;&lt;/Request&gt;</t>', '69383e852b6d82b7755a4ceb24a8953b', 0, '', 'v0uzultr', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(522, 404, 49, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1444034976, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit Must Barrier Crossing', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>bool BarrierCrossing(sTRADE * trade,char *BarrierComponentName){\n	// Execute Barrier Crossing \n	sOPTERMPAR oparm;\n	sCUST_ID counterparty;\n	sRESULTS result;\n\n	memset(&amp;oparm, 0, sizeof(sOPTERMPAR));\n	memset(&amp;counterparty, 0, sizeof(sCUST_ID));\n\n	strcpy(counterparty.Name, trade-&gt;Base.Env-&gt;Cust.Name);\n	oparm.Type = sTA_BARRIER_CROSSING;\n	oparm.TradeDate = sAsOfDate();\n	oparm.EventDate = sMAXUS;\n	oparm.EffDate = sAsOfDate();\n	oparm.counterParty = &amp;counterparty;\n\n	mSetList(oparm.BarrReferenceList.List , sizeof( sBARR_REF_CHANGE ), offsetof(sBARR_REF_CHANGE_LIST , Data ));\n	sBARR_REF_CHANGE barritem;\n	memset(&amp;barritem, 0, sizeof(sBARR_REF_CHANGE));\n	// Must Assign Barrier Component Name\n	strcpy(barritem.CompName.Name,BarrierComponentName);\n	barritem.NeedsCrossing = sYES;\n	sInsertListItem((void*)&amp;oparm.BarrReferenceList, oparm.BarrReferenceList.List.ItemsUsed, (void*) &amp;barritem);\n\n	if (sEntityDoSTDAction(sTradeGetEntity(trade), trade, (void *)&amp;oparm, sACT_BARRIER_CROSSING, 0) != sSUCCESS)\n	{\n		char msg[100];\n		sprintf(msg, \"Do Fully Terminate for Trade %s Failed.\", trade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n		sLogMessage(msg, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n		return false;\n	}\n\n	return true;\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'ac710e507491f17a166d4f88536f2f24', 0, 'AIA=', '3orn0pdk', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(523, 404, 49, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1444035036, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit MUST Full Termination', '<r><CODE><s>[code]</s>bool FullTerminate(sTRADE * trade){\n	// Execute Fully Terminate \n	sOPTERMPAR oparm;\n	sCUST_ID counterparty;\n\n	memset(&amp;oparm, 0, sizeof(sOPTERMPAR));\n	memset(&amp;counterparty, 0, sizeof(sCUST_ID));\n	strcpy(counterparty.Name, trade-&gt;Base.Env-&gt;Cust.Name);\n	oparm.Type = sTA_TERMINATED;\n	oparm.TradeDate = sAsOfDate();\n	oparm.EventDate = sMAXUS;\n	oparm.EffDate = sAsOfDate();\n	oparm.counterParty = &amp;counterparty;\n\n	if (sEntityDoSTDAction(sTradeGetEntity(trade), trade, (void *)&amp;oparm, sACT_FULLTERM, 0) != sSUCCESS)\n	{\n		char msg[100];\n		sprintf(msg, \"Do Fully Terminate for Trade %s Failed.\", trade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n		sLogMessage(msg, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n                return false;\n	}\n	if (sEntityDoSTDAction(sTradeGetEntity(trade), trade, NULL, sACT_SAVE, 0) != sSUCCESS)\n	{\n		char msg[100];\n		sprintf(msg, \"Save Fully Terminate for Trade %s Failed.\", trade-&gt;Base.TradeID.Num);\n		sLogMessage(msg, sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n		return false;\n	}\n\n	return true;\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'de4506e429da705892da89307557eb32', 0, 'AIA=', '33aizia2', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(525, 443, 5, 61, 0, '10.48.1.132', 1444804692, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: 透過eToolKit 執行報表並取得資料', '<t>補充跨Server呼叫eToolKit 的Sample Code.</t>', 'aec6feb278a1fe7abc99274cf7e35e50', 1, '', '1j2idtv7', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(526, 445, 6, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1445325675, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '取得DBML 欄位property 長度判斷寫入資料是否超過定義之長度', '<r>呼叫:\n<CODE><s>[code]</s><i>\n</i>foreach(object insert in db.GetChangeSet().Inserts)\n{\n	FindLongStrings(insert);\n}\n log.Debug(\"List Update\");\nforeach(object update in db.GetChangeSet().Updates)\n{\n	FindLongStrings(update);\n}\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n定義:\n<CODE><s>[code]</s><i>\n</i>private void FindLongStrings(object testObject)\n{\n	foreach(System.Reflection.PropertyInfo propInfo in testObject.GetType().GetProperties())\n	{\n		foreach(ColumnAttribute attribute in propInfo.GetCustomAttributes(\n		typeof(ColumnAttribute),true))\n		{\n			//log.Debug(\"DB Field Type = \"+attribute.DbType.ToLower());\n			if(attribute.DbType.ToLower().Contains(\"varchar\") &amp;&amp; !attribute.DbType.\n			ToLower().Equals(\"varchar(1)\"))\n			{\n				string dbType = attribute.DbType.ToLower();\n				int numberStartIndex = dbType.IndexOf(\"varchar(\") + 8;\n				int numberEndIndex = dbType.IndexOf(\")\",numberStartIndex);\n				string lengthString = dbType.Substring(numberStartIndex,(numberEndIndex-\n				numberStartIndex));\n				int maxLength =0;\n				int.TryParse(lengthString, out maxLength);\n				string currentValue=(string)propInfo.GetValue(testObject,null);\n				if(!string.IsNullOrEmpty(currentValue) &amp;&amp; maxLength !=0 &amp;&amp; currentValue.Length &gt;\n				maxLength)\n				{\n					log.Debug(testObject.GetType().Name +\".\"+propInfo.Name + \" \" + currentValue +\n					\"Max:\" +maxLength);\n				}\n			}\n		}\n	}\n}\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n可參考TR_Web FXO2之Barrier.cs程式</r>', '74435868b05e88a10d65ab73f64e339a', 0, 'AIA=', '2yfg8hwv', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(527, 403, 40, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1445564662, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '修改extacctevent_feib', '<r>修改 mDLLEXPORT int cExtFXCONAD(sTRADE *Trade, sACCTNG_EVENTLIST *AcctngEventL, sACCT_EVTYPE AccEventType)\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>/*----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nNAME            cExtFXCONAD\nSYNOPSIS\nSCOPE           PUBLIC\nSOURCE          extacctevent.cc\nLIBRARY         clientapi\nPURPOSE         External Accounting function for computing cAE_FX_CONAD amount.\nSYNTAX          int cExtFXCONAD(sTRADE *Trade, sACCTNG_EVENTLIST * AcctngEventL,\nsACCT_EVTYPE  AccEventType)\n\nTrade        : Trade to process\n\nAcctngEventL : Accounting Event List to be updated\n\nAccEventType : Accounting Event Type to process\n\nRETURNS         sSUCCESS    Normal completion.\nsERROR      Error occured.\nNOTES           cAE_FX_CONAD =Reversal of Near Leg Notional Amounts on Far leg Settlement Date.\nCcy is the currency of the transaction/leg of the transaction.\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/\nmDLLEXPORT int cExtFXCONAD(sTRADE *Trade, sACCTNG_EVENTLIST *AcctngEventL, sACCT_EVTYPE AccEventType)\n{\n\n	sAMOUNT amount = 0., mainamt = 0., moneyamt = 0., summain = 0., summoney = 0.;\n	sACCTNG_EVENT acctng;\n	int found = 0;\n	sIDATE AsOfDate = AcctngEventL-&gt;Char.AsOfDate;\n	sIDATE valuedate = sMAXUS;\n	sCCY MainCcy;\n	sCCY MoneyCcy;\n	//sXRATE         NearRate;\n\n	// Only process if it is an FXSWAP \n	// sLogMessage(\"Enter\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n	if (Trade-&gt;Base.TradeType == sTT_FXSWAP)\n	{\n		// FX TERMINATION\n		if ((Trade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_PART_TERMINATED) || (Trade-&gt;Base.Back-&gt;TermAssignStatus == sTA_TERMINATED))\n		{\n			sFOREX *forex = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex;\n			sENTITYLIST *fxEventList = &amp;Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;Events;\n			sFXEVENT *pFXEvent = NULL;\n			//         sLogMessage(\"Enter Term\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n			// Determine if Terminations with value date equal to Accounting Asof Date\n			for (int i = 0; i &lt; fxEventList-&gt;List.ItemsUsed; i++)\n			{\n				pFXEvent = (sFXEVENT*)sGetListItem(fxEventList, i);\n				if ((pFXEvent-&gt;FXEvType == sFXEV_TERMINATION) &amp;&amp; (pFXEvent-&gt;Date &lt;= AsOfDate))\n				{\n					// 取得實際Termination Date\n					valuedate = pFXEvent-&gt;Date;\n					// 取得本次提解主幣別金額\n					mainamt = pFXEvent-&gt;Amount1;\n					// 取得本次提解兌換幣別金額\n					moneyamt = pFXEvent-&gt;Amount2;\n					// 主幣別\n					strcpy(MainCcy.Name, pFXEvent-&gt;Ccy1.Name);\n					// 兌換幣別\n					strcpy(MoneyCcy.Name, pFXEvent-&gt;Ccy2.Name);\n					// 提解遠期，所以直接用遠期的金額來判斷本次提解多少金額\n\n					// 判斷主幣別，用來計算主幣別比例\n					if(strcmp(Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtCcy.Name,MainCcy.Name)==0)\n					{\n						moneyamt = (-1. * Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldAmt) * abs(mainamt/ Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtAmt);\n					}\n					else\n					{\n						moneyamt = (-1. * Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtAmt) * abs(mainamt/ Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldAmt);\n					}\n\n					summain = summain + mainamt;\n					summoney = summoney + moneyamt;\n					//               sLogMessage(\"gen new event\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n					// Clear Accounting Event structure for first Ccy\n					sInitAcctngEvent(&amp;acctng, sINIT);\n					// Fill Accounting Event structure\n					acctng.SeqNumber = 1;\n					acctng.Ccy = MainCcy;\n					// 修正更隨遠期方向\n					acctng.Amount = mainamt;\n					acctng.ValueDate = valuedate;\n					acctng.AccType = cAE_FX_CONAD;\n					// Call Standard Toolkit function to add the new accounting event into the list\n					if (sInsertListItem((sACCTNG_EVENTLIST*)AcctngEventL, AcctngEventL-&gt;List.ItemsUsed, (sACCTNG_EVENT*)&amp;acctng))\n					{\n						sLogMessage(\"Error inserting in Accounting Event  list\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n						return (sERROR);\n					}\n\n					// Clear Accounting Event structure for second Ccy\n					sInitAcctngEvent(&amp;acctng, sINIT);\n					// Fill Accounting Event structure\n					acctng.SeqNumber = 1;\n					acctng.Ccy = MoneyCcy;\n					// 修正更隨遠期方向\n					acctng.Amount = moneyamt;\n					acctng.ValueDate = valuedate;\n					acctng.AccType = cAE_FX_CONAD;\n					// Call Standard Toolkit function to add the new accounting event into the list\n					if (sInsertListItem((sACCTNG_EVENTLIST*)AcctngEventL, AcctngEventL-&gt;List.ItemsUsed, (sACCTNG_EVENT*)&amp;acctng))\n					{\n						sLogMessage(\"Error inserting in Accounting Event  list\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n						return (sERROR);\n					}\n				}\n			}\n		}\n		// END OF TERMINATION\n		//      sLogMessage(\"Enter normal\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n		if (Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;ValDate &lt;= AsOfDate)\n		{\n			// Process BoughtAmount first\n			valuedate = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;ValDate;\n\n			// Clear Accounting Event structure\n\n			sInitAcctngEvent(&amp;acctng, sINIT);\n\n			// Fill Accounting Event structure\n\n			acctng.SeqNumber = 1;\n			acctng.Ccy = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtCcy;\n			//acctng.Amount         = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtAmt\n			if (summain &lt; 0)\n			{\n				acctng.Amount = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtAmt + summain;\n			}\n			else\n			{\n				acctng.Amount = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;BoughtAmt + summoney;\n			}\n			acctng.ValueDate = valuedate;\n			acctng.AccType = cAE_FX_CONAD;\n\n			// Call Standard Toolkit function to add the new accounting event into the list\n\n			if (sInsertListItem((sACCTNG_EVENTLIST*)AcctngEventL, AcctngEventL-&gt;List.ItemsUsed, (sACCTNG_EVENT*)&amp;acctng))\n			{\n				sLogMessage(\"Error inserting in Accounting Event  list\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n				return (sERROR);\n			}\n\n			// Process SoldAmount second\n			// Clear Accounting Event structure\n\n			sInitAcctngEvent(&amp;acctng, sINIT);\n\n			// Fill Accounting Event structure\n\n			acctng.SeqNumber = 1;\n			acctng.Ccy = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldCcy;\n			//acctng.Amount         = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldAmt * -1.;\n			if (summain &gt; 0)\n			{\n				acctng.Amount = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldAmt * -1. + summain;\n			}\n			else\n			{\n				acctng.Amount = Trade-&gt;FxTrade.Forex-&gt;SoldAmt * -1. + summoney;\n			}\n			acctng.ValueDate = valuedate;\n			acctng.AccType = cAE_FX_CONAD;\n\n			//Call Standard Toolkit function to add the new accounting event into the list\n\n			if (sInsertListItem((sACCTNG_EVENTLIST*)AcctngEventL, AcctngEventL-&gt;List.ItemsUsed, (sACCTNG_EVENT*)&amp;acctng))\n			{\n				sLogMessage(\"Error inserting in Accounting Event  list\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n				return (sERROR);\n			}\n		}\n	}\n	// sLogMessage(\"Exit\", sLOG_ERROR, 0);\n	return (sSUCCESS);\n}<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'afd0c1af93607d8bb752730d68df5c26', 0, 'AIA=', '1fbufs7r', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(528, 446, 49, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1445825516, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'AresSummit Client Mage 派送檔案製作方式', '<r>請參考附件進行派送程式包裝作業\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"AresSummit Client Mage派送製作方式.docx\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>AresSummit Client Mage派送製作方式.docx<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '72514b6e07e2d0745e739837bcc200ef', 1, 'AAg=', '29hp66a0', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(529, 447, 49, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1446442591, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'STK Help Generate 標準作業', '<r>此作業是在Summit V5.7上面進行<br/>\n1.先將打包的檔案stkhelp.zip 解開後放置於 D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp目錄下\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"stkhelp.zip\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>stkhelp.zip<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n2.修改 D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp\\generator\\config.txt\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"config.txt\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>config.txt<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n3.確認目錄存在<br/>\nD:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp\\generator\\entities (要產生Entity的資訊)<br/>\nD:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp\\StkHelpApplet\\out (產生新的Document)<br/>\n4.準備好新的Include檔案\n<LIST><s>[list]</s><LI>一般來說會建立一個新的資料夾例如 D:\\FEIB57</LI><e>[/list]</e></LIST>\n<LIST><s>[list]</s><LI>將FEIB_REF\\include全部複製到D:\\FEIB57</LI><e>[/list]</e></LIST>\n<LIST><s>[list]</s><LI>將FEIB_REF\\ie全部複製到D:\\FEIB57</LI><e>[/list]</e></LIST>\n5. generate entity information<br/>\n切換到  D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\exe 目錄下<br/>\ndumpentdesc.exe -O D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp\\generator\\entities -ALL<br/>\n<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>記得若執行沒有重又作，請先進行FT的Application Definition 先定義一下dumpentdesc執行檔，讓這個指令可以執行。<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n6. 修改config.txt<br/>\nSUMMIT_FILES_DIRECTORY = D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/StkHelpApplet/needed/<br/>\nINPUT_DIRECTORY = D:\\FEIB57\\<br/>\nOUTPUT_DIRECTORY =  D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/StkHelpApplet/out/<br/>\nENTITIES_DIRECTORY = D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/generator/entities/<br/>\nLOG_FILE = D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/log_file.txt<br/>\n7. 開始進行文件產生<br/>\n<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>建議先將D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/StkHelpApplet/out 目錄下的內容全部進行清空作業<e>[/color]</e></COLOR><br/>\n切換到 D:\\sumapps\\V5.7\\stkhelp\\generator\\entities<br/>\n執行 createEntitiesFilesFile.bat 等一下就可以完成<br/>\n8. 確認完成文件是否正確<br/>\n切換到 D:/sumapps/V5.7/stkhelp/StkHelpApplet/out/ 並查看新產生stkhelp.htm是否存在<br/>\n開啟stkhelp.htm就可以查看新的Help內容<br/>\n<COLOR color=\"#FF00FF\"><s>[color=#FF00FF]</s>注意，在struct內只會看到原廠提供的內容，若要查看新的㯗位必需在原本的Entity頁面下Property List for Entity部份，才可以查看<e>[/color]</e></COLOR></r>', '4dad65fd261b45eeb547a4f237036f23', 1, 'Akg=', '15uwteea', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
