(590, 492, 5, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1516148617, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Swift電文Header從FEINTWTP調整為FEINTWT0', '<t>Summit是透過AresSummitGS將原Summit dispatch出來的電文Header Swift code FEINTWTP 改為 FEINTWT0 <br/>\n所以要取得Swift Code Header 為FEINTWT0的電文，步驟說明下：<br/>\n<br/>\n1.確認AresSummitGS的config內容(D:\\AresSummit\\AresSummitGS\\bin\\config\\ares-gws.properties)<br/>\nFILE.SWIFT.Outgoing=d:/sumapps/dispatch/swift/FEINTWT0/SOut<br/>\nFILE.SWIFT.ValidBIC=FEINTWT0<br/>\n<br/>\n2.啟動Windows AresSummitGS服務<br/>\n<br/>\n3.至D:\\sumapps\\Dispatch\\swift\\FEINTWT0目錄下取得異動Swift code後之電文檔案</t>', '7df30e9b3cfeee821e3d303ee039d62b', 0, '', '2sv41lm2', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
