(602, 310, 20, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1528938686, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: 查詢重覆產生帳務的Script', '<r>經驗證後，只要在資料庫執行下列指令， 就可以很快速的將重覆的帳務列出來。\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>Select min(ID) ID from dmpostingevent \nwhere originalid in (Select originalid from dmpostingevent  group by originalid having  count(originalid) =2) \ngroup by originalid<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n接下來透過文字編輯器製作刪除的指令，範本如下：\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>delete dmpostingevent where ID=\'009N76YH\';<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\n就可以完成移除重覆帳務.<br/>\n<br/>\n使用下列Script來進行刪除，速度會更快\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>delete dmpostingevent where ID in (\nSelect min(ID) ID from dmpostingevent \nwhere originalid in (Select originalid from dmpostingevent  group by originalid having  count(originalid) =2) \ngroup by originalid)\n<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'c4623b7c14030f2c965d18a82428bc10', 0, '', 'pkwssxbf', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(603, 310, 20, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1529092806, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: 查詢重覆產生帳務的Script', '<r>批次目前新增兩支程式如下：<br/>\n<br/>\n記得一定要在<br/>\nP:\\Batch\\sumprod\\Reporting_Results\\<br/>\n建立<COLOR color=\"#FF0000\"><s>[color=#FF0000]</s>DoubleEventCheck<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>目錄，如此才可以正確產生Log<br/>\n<br/>\nDeleteDoubleAccountEvent.cmd 執行會計帳重覆移除作業\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>set SUMMITDB=sumdev\nset oracle_instance=%ORACLE_SID%\nsqlplus %SUMMITDB%/%SUMMITDB%@%oracle_instance% @D:\\sumapps\\Batch\\%SUMMITDB%\\RemoveDoubleAccount.sql<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n\nRemoveDoubleAccount.sql 會計帳重覆移除Script\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>set feedback off\nset verify off\nset linesize 50\nvar filename nvarchar2(30)\nvar schemaname nvarchar2(30)\ncolumn filename new_val filename\ncolumn schemaname new_val schemaname\nSELECT TO_CHAR(sysdate,\'YYYYMMDDHH24MISS\') filename FROM DUAL;\nSELECT DBNAME schemaname FROM DMDB;\nset termout off;\nSpool \"D:\\sumapps\\Batch\\&amp;schemaname\\Reporting_Results\\DoubleEventCheck\\&amp;filename\"\nSelect min(ID) ID from dmpostingevent where originalid in (Select originalid from dmpostingevent  group by originalid having  count(originalid) =2) group by originalid;\n-- Start To Delete\ndelete dmpostingevent where ID in ( Select min(ID) ID from dmpostingevent where originalid in (Select originalid from dmpostingevent  group by originalid having  count(originalid) =2) group by originalid);\ncommit\n/\nspool off\nexit<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', '664a463505866ee9cdca3b0caa44b7f2', 0, '', '2iaee2a0', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(604, 503, 6, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1530561309, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', '透過NuGet Oracle Client 直接連Oracle，不需要安裝Oracle Client程式', '<r>做法如下，請參考。<br/>\n<br/>\n1. 請先安裝Oracle Client程式\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"ODP.NET_Managed_ODAC122cR1.zip\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>ODP.NET_Managed_ODAC122cR1.zip<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n解開後，直接參考您目前系統是32 bit or 64bit進行安裝，安裝方式，請填系統申請單，讓系統組安裝即可。\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_11-00-26.png\" index=\"8\"><s>[attachment=8]</s>2018-07-02_11-00-26.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_11-00-48.png\" index=\"7\"><s>[attachment=7]</s>2018-07-02_11-00-48.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n2. 建立自定的Nuget Package資料夾\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_10-53-15.png\" index=\"3\"><s>[attachment=3]</s>2018-07-02_10-53-15.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n3.將下列檔案放入資料夾\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"NuGetPackages.rar\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>NuGetPackages.rar<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_11-28-44.png\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>2018-07-02_11-28-44.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n4. 於Visual Studio IDE設定NugetPackage自行路徑\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_10-55-04.png\" index=\"6\"><s>[attachment=6]</s>2018-07-02_10-55-04.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_10-56-06.png\" index=\"5\"><s>[attachment=5]</s>2018-07-02_10-56-06.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n4.引用套件後就可以執行了。\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"2018-07-02_10-56-27.png\" index=\"4\"><s>[attachment=4]</s>2018-07-02_10-56-27.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n\n<br/>\n5.範例程式如下：<br/>\n「<COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>深黃色<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>」的部份，請自行改成符合系統的設定，至於設定要放哪裡，我目前寫成變數，其他就自行發揮囉。<br/>\n<br/>\n var dbconnectstring = \"Data Source=(DESCRIPTION=(ADDRESS=(PROTOCOL=tcp)(HOST=<COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>10.48.160.xxx<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>)(PORT=1521))(CONNECT_DATA=(SERVICE_NAME=<COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>DBInstance<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>)));Persist Security Info=True;User ID=<COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>id<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>;Password=<COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>password<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>\";<br/>\n            using (OracleConnection conn = new OracleConnection(dbconnectstring))<br/>\n            {<br/>\n                if (conn.State == System.Data.ConnectionState.Closed)<br/>\n                {<br/>\n                    conn.Open();<br/>\n                }<br/>\n<br/>\n                string SQL_cmd = \"Select * from <COLOR color=\"#FFBF00\"><s>[color=#FFBF00]</s>TestEnv<e>[/color]</e></COLOR>\";<br/>\n<br/>\n                OracleCommand cmd = new OracleCommand(SQL_cmd, conn);<br/>\n                OracleDataAdapter dataadapter = new OracleDataAdapter();<br/>\n                dataadapter.SelectCommand = cmd;<br/>\n                DataSet ds = new DataSet();<br/>\n                dataadapter.Fill(ds);<br/>\n                if (conn.State == System.Data.ConnectionState.Open)<br/>\n                {<br/>\n                    conn.Close();<br/>\n                }<br/>\n            }</r>', '07385e25adf8e16aaa9395a54c495f5e', 1, '', '2owp5wrx', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(605, 475, 6, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1535417323, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: Logger Server介紹', '<r>定義C# Classs 訊息\n<CODE><s>[code]</s> public class LogItem\n    {\n        // LogID\n        public int LogID { get; set; }\n        // 系統名稱\n        public string ApplicationType { get; set; }\n        // 使用者帳號\n        public string UserID { get; set; }\n        // 使用者來源\n        public string Source { get; set; }\n        // 所連線目標IP\n        public string ConnectIP { get; set; }\n        // 所存取之檔案/物件名稱\n        public string AccessObj { get; set; }\n        //所存取帳號\n        public string AccessID { get; set; }\n        // 程式/交易名稱\n        public string ProgramName { get; set; }\n        //動作類別\n        public string ActionType { get; set; }\n        //執行參數/語法\n        public string ExeCommand { get; set; }\n        //異動前後值\n        public string BeforeUpdate { get; set; }\n        //執行結果內容\n        public string ExeResult { get; set; }\n        //日期時間\n        public DateTime Createtime { get; set; }\n        //備註資料\n        public object MemoData { get; set; }\n    }<e>[/code]</e></CODE>\n將訊息透過WebAPI寫入\n<CODE><s>[code]</s>// 定義 Logger所需要記錄的資訊\n            LogItem item = new LogItem();\n            item.ApplicationType = txtApplicationType.Text;\n            item.UserID = txtUserID.Text;\n            item.Source = txtSource.Text;\n            item.ConnectIP = txtConnectIP.Text;\n            item.AccessObj = txtAccessObj.Text;\n            item.AccessID = txtAccessID.Text;\n            item.ProgramName = txtProgramName.Text;\n            item.ActionType = txtActionType.Text;\n            item.ExeCommand = txtExeCommand.Text;\n            item.BeforeUpdate = txtBeforeUpdate.Text;\n            item.ExeResult = txtExeResult.Text;\n            item.MemoData = txtMemoData.Text;\n\n            // Serialize 訊息成 JSON模式\n            string ItemStr = JsonConvert.SerializeObject(item, Formatting.Indented);\n\n            // 取得Request網址http://10.48.160.48/LogServer/api/Logger\n            var webRequest = System.Net.WebRequest.Create(Properties.Settings.Default.LoggerAPIUrl);\n            if (webRequest != null)\n            {\n                // 定義型態為POST\n                webRequest.Method = \"POST\";\n                //webRequest.Timeout = Convert.ToInt32(txtTimeOut.Text);\n                webRequest.ContentType = \"application/json\";\n\n                // 將Serialize 訊息成 JSON模式轉成Byte模式\n                byte[] buffer = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(ItemStr);\n                // 定義需傳送訊息長度\n                webRequest.ContentLength = buffer.Length;\n                // 定義即將寫入的資料流\n                var reqStream = webRequest.GetRequestStream();\n                // 進行寫入作業\n                reqStream.Write(buffer, 0, buffer.Length);\n\n                //reqStream.Close();\n                try\n                {\n                    // 開啟網站回傳訊息\n                    using (var response = (System.Net.HttpWebResponse)webRequest.GetResponse())\n                    {\n                        // 判斷網站寫入後是否回傳Request寫入正確，並回傳OK訊息\n                        if (response.StatusCode == System.Net.HttpStatusCode.OK)\n                        {\n                            // 定義Stream準備接收網頁回傳訊息\n                            using (System.IO.Stream s = response.GetResponseStream())\n                            {\n                                using (System.IO.StreamReader sr = new System.IO.StreamReader(s))\n                                {\n                                    // 將回傳訊息轉成文字\n                                    string ReturnStr = sr.ReadToEnd();\n                                }\n                            }\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n                catch (WebException webex)\n                {\n                    var webResponse = webex.Response as System.Net.HttpWebResponse;\n\n                    if (webResponse != null)\n                    {\n                        MessageBox.Show(((int)webResponse.StatusCode).ToString() + \"-\" + webResponse.StatusCode.ToString());\n                    }\n                }\n            }<e>[/code]</e></CODE></r>', 'cee24339126850e4dbf4827c519f72c7', 0, '', '35bwyxqg', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
(606, 366, 48, 59, 0, '10.48.2.140', 1548182327, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: AresSummit Batch gleod驗證成功', '<t>Run : <br/>\n差異是條件有 ExtractFlag = \'N\' , 每次執行完都會更新成 Y , 只會執行沒處理過的 dmPostingEvent<br/>\nselect * from dmPOSTINGEVENT where (location=\'%s\' or accountid like \'%s%%\') and postingdate=\'%s\' and accountid not in (\'CASH_SUSPENSE\',\'SUSPENSE\',\'DUMMYCASH\',\'DUMMY\',\'CONTROL\',\'NETTING\',\'CASH_CONTROL\', \'OBUCONTRAINBR\', \'DBUCONTRAINBR\', \'OBUINTERBR\', \'DBUINTERBR\',\'INTERBR\',\'CONTRAINBR\') and extractflag=\'N\' and not accountId like \'DUM%%\'<br/>\n<br/>\nRerun :<br/>\n差異是條件沒有 ExtractFlag , 會執行所有 dmPostingEvent, 若本來是 ExtractFlag = \'N\'  則更新成 Yselect * from dmPOSTINGEVENT where (location=\'%s\' or accountid like \'%s%%\') and postingdate=\'%s\' and accountid not in (\'CASH_SUSPENSE\',\'SUSPENSE\',\'DUMMYCASH\',\'DUMMY\',\'CONTROL\',\'NETTING\',\'CASH_CONTROL\', \'OBUCONTRAINBR\', \'DBUCONTRAINBR\', \'OBUINTERBR\', \'DBUINTERBR\',\'INTERBR\',\'CONTRAINBR\') and not accountId like \'DUM%%\'</t>', 'c220e5a8232c60fd4479cc1f0226bb6e', 0, '', '1b1o23kg', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
