(615, 510, 5, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1561156064, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Summit Token Function List', '<t>交易使用<br/>\n1.cFillLegSpotFwdCriteria<br/>\nTradeType: FX Trade <br/>\nFXSPOT TokenValue = SPOT<br/>\nFXSWAP TokenValue = FWD SPOT<br/>\nFXFWD TokenValue = FWD SPOT<br/>\n<br/>\n2.cFillCustGroup<br/>\n傳回Customer GroupID<br/>\nCustomer GroupID<br/>\n<br/>\n3.cFillGuaranteed<br/>\n判斷 Security 的 Issuer or Guarantor 前四個字元為FETP 或 CBC<br/>\nTokenValue = Y N<br/>\n<br/>\n4.cFillSecRated<br/>\n判斷Customer ISSUE RATED <br/>\nTradeType: BOND<br/>\nTokenValue = Y N<br/>\n<br/>\n5.cFillRepoSecType<br/>\n傳回COLLATERAL的SECType<br/>\nTradeType: REPO<br/>\nTokenValue = COLLATERAL的SECType SecType<br/>\n<br/>\n6.cFillContractID<br/>\n回傳ContractID<br/>\nTradeType: FUTURE<br/>\nTokenValue = ContractID<br/>\n<br/>\n7.cFillCcyAssetLocalOther<br/>\nFill Ccy value for Asset. If Ccy is Base Ccy, then BASE, if Ccy is other, then OTH<br/>\n僅有Asset才可以使用<br/>\n判斷幣別是否為本位幣<br/>\nTokenValue = BASE OTH<br/>\n<br/>\n8.cFillMTMSpotFwdCriteria<br/>\n比較ValueDate 和 SpotDate<br/>\nTradeType: FX SWAP<br/>\nTokenValue = FWD SPOT<br/>\n<br/>\n9.cCheckMMTradeTerm<br/>\n依照提解是判斷<br/>\nTradeType: MM<br/>\nTokenValue = ST MT LT<br/>\n<br/>\n10.cIsCNH<br/>\n判斷是否為CNH 或 CNY<br/>\nTradeType: DEAL_PAYMENT MM FXTRADE FXOPTION<br/>\nTokenValue = Y N<br/>\n<br/>\n11.cMustCustGroupIdentity<br/>\nTradeType: MUST<br/>\n當\"premium &gt; 0 \" 則Token value: S<br/>\n當\"premium &lt; 0 \" 則Token value: B<br/>\n當\"premium = 0 \" 則 CustGrp = 1-6 Token value: S<br/>\n其他皆為 B<br/>\n<br/>\n12.cMustPremCcyLocIdentity<br/>\nTradeType: MUST<br/>\n當 premium Ccy = sBaseCcy 就回傳BASE<br/>\n當 premium Ccy != sBaseCcy 就回傳OTH<br/>\nTokenValue = BASE OTH<br/>\n<br/>\n13.cFillSecRatedSwap<br/>\n判斷Customer ISSUE RATED <br/>\nTradeType: SWAP<br/>\nTokenValue = Y N<br/>\n<br/>\n部位使用<br/>\n1.cFillCcyLocalOther<br/>\n判斷幣別是否為本位幣<br/>\nTokenValue = BASE OTH<br/>\n<br/>\n2.cFillPosGuaranted<br/>\n判斷 Security 的 Issuer or Guarantor 前四個字元為FETP 或 CBC<br/>\nTokenValue = Y N<br/>\n<br/>\n3.cFillPosRated<br/>\n判斷Customer ISSUE RATED <br/>\nTokenValue = Y N</t>', '0c22bba053a9563e82e716db77de1524', 0, '', 'zxhxc93r', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
