(621, 225, 36, 58, 0, '10.48.1.120', 1574301511, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'Re: 新增plupd -U 時，儲存所需之Summit Table資料', '<t>目前會需要建立的有以下內容，於Summit AP 與DB升級後，需手動增加<br/>\n<br/>\nPS:用前需先設定ORACLE_HOME設定至環境變數中<br/>\ncd D:\\sumapps\\V62\\etc\\scripts\\ORACLE<br/>\necho sumprod &gt;smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod DTD -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod DTD_DBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod DTD_OBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod DTD_HK -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\n<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MTD -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MTD_DBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MTD_OBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MTD_HK -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MTD_FX -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\n<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod YTD -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod YTD_DBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod YTD_OBU -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod YTD_FX -p smdbprodpwd.txt<br/>\n<br/>\nsh o_createPNLtable.sh smdbprod sumprod MO -p smdbprodpwd.txt</t>', '002d98659b18084e8efa70cda3951cd0', 0, '', 'spn62wmh', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
