(623, 516, 35, 53, 0, '10.48.2.73', 1576869887, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'MT300合併電文', '<r>After checking with our experts, it is advised that there is a PC request done for fx swap trade which causes double inception of FX Swap Trade (and only for FXSwap) be introduced in V5.5.<br/>\nIt is related to the fact that for FXSwap Trade with CLS, you can have one leg CLS and one leg Swift.  So the choice has been done to have one message par leg (Near Leg / Far Leg) for FXSwap Trade when Carrier are Swift /CLS.<br/>\n<br/>\nStarting V55, there is a fork in DocumentServer.xml dedicated to that part : DocumentServer_wfd.xml   IsFXSwapInception.<br/>\n<br/>\nTo let summit generate one MT300 for fx swap trade, I have done following changes:<br/>\nEdit DocumentServer_wfd.xml and commented the &lt;label id = “FXSwapProcessing”&gt;. The testing result is positive, one MT300 is generated with customization template.<br/>\n<br/>\nPlease test in your side and let me know if you have any problems. Attached please find relevant screen shot and an commented DocumentServer_wfd.xml for your reference.<br/>\n<br/>\nV57 <ATTACHMENT filename=\"dispatchserver_wfd.xml\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>dispatchserver_wfd.xml<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\nV62 <ATTACHMENT filename=\"documentserver_wfd.xml\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>documentserver_wfd.xml<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', 'aa067183901a88b5cdf9f1f4bba69083', 1, '', '3hcjvlhq', 1, 0, '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, '', 0),
