(642, 531, 65, 62, 0, '10.48.2.177', 1590719623, 0, 1, 1, 1, 1, '', 'FETP 假上手設定 Step', '<r>1.) Stop UptradeAPI(27373) service, and copy “VerBank-ApiStation-Allone-Artificial” into tomcat\\webapps\\<br/>\n    1.1) Check below settings in config.properties<br/>\n        ** logPath<br/>\n        ** quoteServPort<br/>\n        ** apiServPort<br/>\n        ** bankName<br/>\n        ** maxInstrument\n <ATTACHMENT filename=\"01.png\" index=\"8\"><s>[attachment=8]</s>01.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n    1.2) Check excludeInst.xml for subscribe instrument.\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"011.png\" index=\"6\"><s>[attachment=6]</s>011.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n    1.3) Check lastQuotes.xml for instrument setting.\n <ATTACHMENT filename=\"012.png\" index=\"5\"><s>[attachment=5]</s>012.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n2.) Stop Uptrade(27333) service, and copy “Allone-Artificial” into VerBank-Uptrade\\WEB-INF\\config\\source<br/>\n	2.1) Check below settings in config.properties<br/>\n		** ipAddress<br/>\n		** servPort (same with apiServPort)\n <ATTACHMENT filename=\"02.png\" index=\"7\"><s>[attachment=7]</s>02.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n	2.2) Check VerBank-Uptrade\\WEB-INF\\config\\config.xml.\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"03.png\" index=\"4\"><s>[attachment=4]</s>03.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n3.) Check uptradeBank records in [UptradeBank] table.\n <ATTACHMENT filename=\"031.png\" index=\"2\"><s>[attachment=2]</s>031.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n4.) Turn on new Uptrade-Bank in Dealer=&gt;Uptrade.\n <ATTACHMENT filename=\"032.png\" index=\"1\"><s>[attachment=1]</s>032.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT>\n5.) Start Uptrade(27333) service.<br/>\n6.) Execute tomcat\\bin\\start.bat which include “VerBank-ApiStation-Allone-Artificial” module, and instrument show “requested”.(UptradeAPI service not running!)\n<ATTACHMENT filename=\"041.png\" index=\"0\"><s>[attachment=0]</s>041.png<e>[/attachment]</e></ATTACHMENT></r>', '55b846c8daea8f64dbaaed